Division and modulus operators satisfy the following property:
given a
.RI dividend\~ a
and a
.RI divisor\~ b ,
a
.RI quotient\~ q
formed by
.RB \[lq] "(a / b)" \[rq]
and a
.RI remainder\~ r
by
.RB \[lq] "(a % b)" \[rq],
