.\" ====================================================================
.SS "Underlining by overstriking with \[rs](ul"
.\" ====================================================================
.
The
.B \[rs]z
escape sequence writes a glyph without advancing the
drawing position,
enabling overstriking.
.
Thus,
.BI \[rs]z c \[rs](ul
formats
.I c
with an underrule glyph on top of it.
.
